he 5 best features in Apple's iOS 5|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-09|last=deAgonia|first=Michael|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619211818/http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|archive-date=2017-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。用戶可以透過iCloud服務同步行事曆、照片、文件、應用程式資料、電子書、聯絡資訊及提醒事項等至所有已登入iCloud的裝置<ref name=":10" /><ref name="iCloud for devs">{{cite web|url=https://developer.apple.com/icloud|title=iCloud for Developers|accessdate=|date=|last=|first=|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|website=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529042429/https://developer.apple.com/icloud/|archive-date=2016-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="PC World 5 features2">{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|title=The 5 best features in Apple's iOS 5|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-09|last=deAgonia|first=Michael|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619211818/http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|archive-date=2017-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1162647/icloud_to_make_official_debut_on_october_12.html|title=iCloud to make official debut on October 12|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-10-04|last=Caldwell|first=Serenity|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723012218/http://www.macworld.com/article/1162647/icloud_to_make_official_debut_on_october_12.html|archive-date=2017-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。用戶還可以備份裝置資料至iCloud，並在重置或更換新裝置後還原資料<ref name="Backup and restore">{{cite web|url=http://support.apple.com/kb/HT4859|title=iCloud: Backup and Restore Overview|accessdate=|date=2014-02-17|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922012427/http://support.apple.com/kb/ht4859|archive-date=2012-09-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/en-gb/HT207428|title=What does iCloud back up?|accessdate=2017-04-01|publisher=Apple|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402083531/https://support.apple.com/en-gb/HT207428|archive-date=2017-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，iCloud還提供了[[查找我的iPhone|尋找我的iPhone]]服務（依裝置不同又被稱為尋找我的iPad、尋找我的iPod及尋找我的Mac），用戶可以透過登入iCloud的裝置及iCloud網站尋找遺失的裝置<ref name=":10" /><ref name="Find My iPhone update on Mac World">{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2010104/hands-on-with-updated-find-my-friends-and-find-my-iphone.html|title=Mac World – Find My iPhone update|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024021235/http://www.macworld.com/article/2010104/hands-on-with-updated-find-my-friends-and-find-my-iphone.html|archive-date=2012-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Find My iPhone with iCloud">{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/icloud/#find|title=iCloud – Find My iPhone|accessdate=2012-11-08|publisher=Apple Inc|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107033022/http://www.apple.com/iphone/icloud/#find|archive-date=2012-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Find My iPhone by Huffington Post">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/10/13/icloud-find-my-iphone_n_1009425.html|title=Find My iPhone – Huffington Post|accessdate=2012-11-08|author=Gilbert, Jason|date=2011-10-13|publisher=Huffington Post|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905131124/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/10/13/icloud-find-my-iphone_n_1009425.html|archive-date=2012-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="iMore review">{{cite web|url=https://www.imore.com/ios-5-iphone-ipad-walkthrough|title=iOS 5 review|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-12|last=Ritchie|first=Rene|website=iMore|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170509181747/http://www.imore.com/ios-5-iphone-ipad-walkthrough|archive-date=2017-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，必要時甚至可以清除其資料<ref name="Find My iPhone gets email notifications and offline device removal by 9to5Mac">{{cite web|url=http://9to5mac.com/2011/06/06/find-my-iphone-gets-email-notifications-offline-device-removal/|title=Find My iPhone gets email notifications and offline device removal – 9to5Mac|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023952/http://9to5mac.com/2011/06/06/find-my-iphone-gets-email-notifications-offline-device-removal/|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Find My iPhone with iCloud2">{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/icloud/#find|title=iCloud – Find My iPhone|accessdate=2012-11-08|publisher=Apple Inc|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107033022/http://www.apple.com/iphone/icloud/#find|archive-date=2012-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 通知中心 ===
{{see also|通知中心}}在iOS 5之前的iOS版本中，通知會以對話框形式出現，強制暫停使用者活動，造成用戶困擾<ref name=":12">{{Cite news|url=http://mark528.pixnet.net/blog/post/14517967-iphone%EF%BC%9Aios5-%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%A5%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83|title=iPhone：iOS5 推撥通知中心 @ 狐的窩 :: 痞客邦 ::|last=(mark528)|first=mark528|newspaper=狐的窩|accessdate=2018-07-27|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729084356/http://mark528.pixnet.net/blog/post/14517967-iphone%EF%BC%9Aios5-%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%A5%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83|archive-date=2018-07-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":13">{{Cite news|url=http://blog.xuite.net/vexed/tech/52870995-iOS+5+%E9%96%8B%E5%95%9F%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83|title=iOS 5 開啟通知中心|last=(vexed)|first=Vexed|newspaper=隨意窩 Xuite日誌|accessdate=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120919074721/http://blog.xuite.net/vexed/tech/52870995-iOS+5+%E9%96%8B%E5%95%9F%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83|archive-date=2012-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在iOS 5中，應用程式及系統通知會短暫顯示在螢幕上方，然後整合至通知中心<ref name=":11" /><ref name="PC World 5 features6" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://iphone.duowan.com/zhuanti/ios5/|title=iOS 5 全新功能介绍及固件下载 - 多玩iPhone中文网|accessdate=2018-07-27|work=iphone.duowan.com|language=zh-cn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102052119/http://iphone.duowan.com/zhuanti/ios5/|archive-date=2016-01-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。用戶隨後可以從上部螢幕邊緣向下拉存取通知中心面板<ref name=":12" /><ref name=":13" />。用戶也可以藉由設定關閉通知中心<ref name=":10" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1160366/ios5_notifications.html|title=First Look: iOS 5 notifications|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-07|last=Friedman|first=Lex|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170429012717/http://www.macworld.com/article/1160366/ios5_notifications.html|archive-date=2017-04-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="PC World 5 features">{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|title=The 5 best features in Apple's iOS 5|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-09|last=deAgonia|first=Michael|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619211818/http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|archive-date=2017-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 無線升級 ===
在iOS 5推出之前，要更新系統或啟用新裝置，都只能透過[[iTunes|iTunes]]電腦端處理<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1163060/up_close_with_ios_5_wireless_syncing_and_updating.html|title=Up close with iOS 5: Wireless syncing and updating|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-10-15|last=Caldwell|first=Serenity|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808112956/http://www.macworld.com/article/1163060/up_close_with_ios_5_wireless_syncing_and_updating.html|archive-date=2017-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>；iOS 5引入了無線升級機能，可以透過網路直接下載更新檔至裝置中並更新，及啟用新裝置<ref name=":10" /><ref name="PC World 5 features6" /><ref name="iMore review" />。

=== 社群媒體整合 ===
在iOS 5中，整合了[[社群媒體|社群媒體]][[Twitter|推特]]的相關功能。用戶可以直接透過系統選單登入推特帳號；相片應用程式、[[Safari|Safari]]及內建[[YouTube|YouTube]]及[[Google_Maps|Google Maps]]應用程式中也出現了[[Twitter|推文]]的選項<ref name=":10" /><ref name="iMore review" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1162993/up_close_with_ios_5_twitter_integration.html|title=Up close with iOS 5: Twitter integration|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-10-13|last=Friedman|first=Lex|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919232616/https://www.macworld.com/article/1162993/up_close_with_ios_5_twitter_integration.html|archive-date=2017-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2011/06/06/apple-twitter-ios5/|title=Apple Blesses Twitter, Makes It the Social Network on iOS Devices|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-07|last=Van Grove|first=Jennifer|website=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430174307/http://mashable.com/2011/06/06/apple-twitter-ios5/|archive-date=2017-04-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 多工處理手勢 ===
在iOS 5中，為[[iPad|iPad]]引進了多工處理手勢，用戶可以通過手指及手勢的變化，使用原本需要繁複操作的功能，包括切換應用程式、顯示多工介面及跳回主畫面等。原本多工處理手勢僅限[[iPad_2|iPad 2]]可以使用<ref name=":10" />，後來延伸支援至[[IPad_(第一代)|第一代iPad]]<ref name="iMore review" />。

=== 鍵盤 ===
在iOS 5中，為iPad引入了浮動鍵盤及分離鍵盤的功能：浮動鍵盤可以使鍵盤向上移動些許、分離鍵盤可以將鍵盤分成兩半，方便輸入文字<ref name=":10" /><ref name="iMore review" />。

== 應用程式新增功能 ==

===相機===
在iOS 5中，在鎖定螢幕增加了相機捷徑。用戶可以於鎖定螢幕出現時點按兩下主畫面按鍵，並點選出現的相機捷徑以開啟相機應用程式<ref name=":10" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.infoworld.com/article/2735900/mobile/ios-5-camera-lock-screen.html|title=iOS 5 camera lock screen|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-21|last=Lynch|first=Jim|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[InfoWorld|InfoWorld]]}}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="MacRumors camera">{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2011/10/13/ios-5-camera-volume-shutter-lock-screen-remote-triggering/|title=iOS 5 Camera: Volume Shutter, Lock Screen, Remote Triggering|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-13|last=Golson|first=Jordan|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102080156/http://www.macrumors.com/2011/10/13/ios-5-camera-volume-shutter-lock-screen-remote-triggering/|archive-date=2017-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2011/06/06/apple-adds-camera-shortcut-to-lock-screen-volume-up-shutter-key/|title=Apple iOS 5 adds instant camera access from lock screen and shutter release to volume-up button|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-06-06|last=Wollman|first=Dana|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101231647/https://www.engadget.com/2011/06/06/apple-adds-camera-shortcut-to-lock-screen-volume-up-shutter-key/|archive-date=2017-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。iOS 5.1更新則去除了點按主畫面按鍵的步驟，改為自螢幕下緣向上拉<ref name="iMore review" /><ref name="CNET camera">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/access-the-iphone-camera-from-the-lock-screen-even-quicker-on-ios-5-1/|title=Access the iPhone camera from the lock screen even quicker on iOS 5.1|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2012-03-08|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180312144951/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/access-the-iphone-camera-from-the-lock-screen-even-quicker-on-ios-5-1/|archive-date=2018-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在iOS 5中，用戶可以使用向上音量控制鍵拍攝相片<ref name="MacRumors camera2">{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2011/10/13/ios-5-camera-volume-shutter-lock-screen-remote-triggering/|title=iOS 5 Camera: Volume Shutter, Lock Screen, Remote Triggering|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-13|last=Golson|first=Jordan|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102080156/http://www.macrumors.com/2011/10/13/ios-5-camera-volume-shutter-lock-screen-remote-triggering/|archive-date=2017-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>；相機應用程式也經過重新設計，新增剪裁、增強亮度及旋轉相片等編輯功能，並可以把照片新增至自定義相簿中<ref name=":15" /><ref name="MacRumors camera2" />。

=== 訊息 ===
{{see also|iMessage}}
在iOS 5中，首次引入[[即時通訊|即時聊天服務]]iMessage，免費提供所有搭載iOS 5以上版本的裝置使用<ref name=":10" /><ref name="PC World 5 features6" /><ref name="iMore review" /><ref name=":16">{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2011/06/07/walkthrough-of-apples-imessages-in-ios-5/|title=Walkthrough of Apple's iMessage in iOS 5|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-07|last=Kim|first=Arnold|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201035045/https://www.macrumors.com/2011/06/07/walkthrough-of-apples-imessages-in-ios-5/|archive-date=2017-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。用戶可以透過iMessage向其他iOS 5裝置用戶傳送文字、照片、影像、定位及聯絡資訊等，還可以確認對方已讀與否<ref name="PC World 5 features6" /><ref name=":16" />。值得一提的是，與普通[[簡訊|簡訊]]不同，iMessage並非透過[[短信|SMS]]服務，而是[[互联网|網際網路]]傳送訊息<ref name=":10" /><ref name="PC World 5 features6" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1162984/ios-apps/ios-5-imessage.html|title=Up close with iOS 5: iMessage|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-10-12|last=Caldwell|first=Serenity|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170603165156/http://www.macworld.com/article/1162984/ios-apps/ios-5-imessage.html|archive-date=2017-06-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2011/06/07/walkthrough-of-apples-imessages-in-ios-5/|title=Walkthrough of Apple's iMessage in iOS 5|accessdate=2017-06-14|date=2011-06-07|last=Kim|first=Arnold|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201035045/https://www.macrumors.com/2011/06/07/walkthrough-of-apples-imessages-in-ios-5/|archive-date=2017-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 提醒事項 ===
{{see also|提醒事項}}
在iOS 5中，首次引入提醒事項服務。用戶可以自由建立提醒事項<ref name=":10" /><ref name="iMore review" /><ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1162991/up_close_with_ios_5_reminders.html|title=Up close with iOS 5: Reminders|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-13|last=Friedman|first=Lex|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610144152/http://www.macworld.com/article/1162991/up_close_with_ios_5_reminders.html|archive-date=2017-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>；應用程式還可以自動偵測識別位置和時間，當進入指定的位置時作出提醒<ref name=":10" /><ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-ios-5-reminders-app/|title=How to use the iOS 5 Reminders app|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-09-13|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220033405/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-ios-5-reminders-app/|archive-date=2018-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===Safari===
{{see also|Safari}}
在iOS 5中，為Safari增加了閱讀列表功能<ref name=":10" /><ref name=":17">{{Cite news|url=https://imtx.me/archives/1502.html|title=改变阅读习惯的Safari 5阅读器！|newspaper=I'm TualatriX|accessdate=2018-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712075806/http://imtx.me/archives/1502.html|archive-date=2015-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。用戶將網頁加入到閱讀列表後，系統會把已閱讀的網址分類，並會透過[[iCloud|iCloud]]同步至其他[[iOS|iOS]]裝置<ref name=":10" /><ref name=":17" />。此外，還新增了閱讀器功能，開啟後系統會自動消除不必要的廣告<ref name=":10" /><ref name=":17" />；不過此功能僅限在iPad中使用，而且並不是所有網頁都適用此功能。除此之外，還增加了私密瀏覽及分頁瀏覽等功能<ref name=":10" /><ref name="iMore review" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shushao.com/tutorial/level5/skill/item/27005-safari|title=怎样开启 iOS 5私密浏览Safari？|date=2011-09-22|publisher=树梢 - 教程 - 玩转iPhone - 相关技巧|language=zh-cn|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111012065107/http://www.shushao.com/tutorial/level5/skill/item/27005-safari|archivedate=2011-10-12|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2011-10-10}}</ref>。

=== 郵件 ===
在iOS 5中，郵件提供了對[[格式化文本|格式化文本的]]支援<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-new-mail-app-in-ios-5/|title=How to use the new Mail app in iOS 5|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-13|last=Profis|first=Sharon|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214182957/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-new-mail-app-in-ios-5/|archive-date=2017-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1163008/up_close_with_ios_5_mails_changes.html|title=Up close with iOS 5: Mail's changes|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-13|last=Frakes|first=Dan|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313164348/http://www.macworld.com/article/1163008/up_close_with_ios_5_mails_changes.html|archive-date=2017-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

