== 問題 ==

=== 系統升級問題 ===
iOS 5在正式推出時，遭遇到了許多與系統升級相關的問題，包括更新伺服器超載當機及更新時發生錯誤等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thenextweb.com/apple/2011/10/12/apples-ios-5-upgrade-servers-are-slammed-causing-3200-or-internal-error-update-issues/|title=iOS 5 Error 3200 or “internal error” update issues? Apple’s servers are getting slammed. [Updated]|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-12|last=Panzarino|first=Matthew|website=The Next Web|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810170842/https://thenextweb.com/apple/2011/10/12/apples-ios-5-upgrade-servers-are-slammed-causing-3200-or-internal-error-update-issues/|archive-date=2017-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/updating-to-ios-5-2011-10|title=Updating To iOS 5 Has Been A Massive Headache|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-12|last=Love|first=Dylan|publisher=[[Axel_Springer_SE|Axel Springer SE]]|website=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810171846/http://www.businessinsider.com/updating-to-ios-5-2011-10|archive-date=2017-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2011/10/12/apple_ios_update_woes|title=iOS update woes prompt gnashing of teeth for Apple fans|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-10-12|last=Goodin|first=Dan|publisher=Situation Publishing|website=[[The_Register|The Register]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810171456/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2011/10/12/apple_ios_update_woes|archive-date=2017-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== iPhone 4S效能問題 ===
iOS 5更新造成部分[[iPhone_4S|iPhone 4S]]效能下降及通話問題，雖然蘋果在隨後的iOS 5.0.1更新修補漏洞，但仍使部分用戶不滿<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":18" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/apple/2011/11/apple-iphone-4s-battery-issues-due-to-ios-5-bugs-update-coming/|title=Apple: iPhone 4S battery issues due to iOS 5 bugs, update coming|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-11-02|last=Cheng|first=Jacqui|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422120725/http://arstechnica.com/apple/2011/11/apple-iphone-4s-battery-issues-due-to-ios-5-bugs-update-coming/|archive-date=2016-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2011/11/iphone-4s-battery-issues/|title=Apple confirms battery life problems are iOS 5 related|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-11-01|last=Bonnington|first=Christina|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Wired_(website)|Wired]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222035736/https://www.wired.com/2011/11/iphone-4s-battery-issues//|archive-date=2017-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2011/11/10/apple-fixes-critical-iphone-battery-issues-with-ios-5-0-1/|title=Apple Fixes Critical iPhone Battery Issues With iOS 5.0.1|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-11-10|last=Parr|first=Ben|website=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907110844/http://mashable.com/2011/11/10/apple-fixes-critical-iphone-battery-issues-with-ios-5-0-1/|archive-date=2017-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Wi-Fi連線問題 ===
iOS 5更新造成部分裝置出現Wi-Fi連線問題。隨然蘋果推出更新試圖補救，但成效不彰。[[Engadget|Engadget]]編輯表示：「iOS 5.0.1更新並未解決問題。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2011/11/21/thanks-to-ios-5-some-users-lose-wifi-connectivity/|title=Thanks to iOS 5, some users lose WiFi connectivity|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-11-21|last=Lutz|first=Zachary|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004085940/https://www.engadget.com/2011/11/21/thanks-to-ios-5-some-users-lose-wifi-connectivity/|archive-date=2017-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 通話問題 ===
iOS 5更新造成部分裝置SIM卡無法使用，還造成部分iPhone 4S通話時莫名出現回音<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/11/11/17/users_report_sim_card_issues_with_apples_iphone_4s_and_ios_5_0_1.html|title=Users report SIM card issues with Apple's iPhone 4S and iOS 5.0.1|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-11-17|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004034715/http://appleinsider.com/articles/11/11/17/users_report_sim_card_issues_with_apples_iphone_4s_and_ios_5_0_1.html|archive-date=2017-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/11/12/16/new_ios_build_meant_to_fix_iphone_4s_sim_card_issues.html|title=New iOS build meant to fix iPhone 4S SIM card issues|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-12-16|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004034843/http://appleinsider.com/articles/11/12/16/new_ios_build_meant_to_fix_iphone_4s_sim_card_issues.html|archive-date=2017-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蘋果隨後於iOS 5.0.1更新修補漏洞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bgr.com/2011/11/01/audio-echo-bug-plagues-iphone-4s-owners-during-voice-calls/|title=Audio echo bug plagues iPhone 4S owners during voice calls|accessdate=2013-08-16|date=2011-11-01|last=Epstein|first=Zach|publisher=BGR|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609173042/http://bgr.com/2011/11/01/audio-echo-bug-plagues-iphone-4s-owners-during-voice-calls/|archive-date=2013-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/iphone-4s-owners-complain-of-persistent-echo/|title=iPhone 4S owners complain of persistent echo|accessdate=2017-06-17|date=2011-11-17|last=Mack|first=Eric|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180408010421/https://www.cnet.com/news/iphone-4s-owners-complain-of-persistent-echo/|archive-date=2018-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

